      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-[var(--ink)] leading-tight">What Happens When Your AI Team Has a Budget</h1>
      <p class="text-[var(--ink-mute)] mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">Give an agent team a budget and everything changes. Not just money. A token budget, a time budget, an action budget. Constraints create accountability. Without budgets, agents waste resources and never learn efficiency. With budgets, they optimize.</p>
